line and asks, "Excuse me, but you don't sound American, where are you
calling from?"...

You say... "erm, er [looking at the CC number] - dunno?"

And off you are kicked, plus the number becomes invalid.

or you could have said this:

"I'm visiting a friend over here at the moment and I have got permission
from my friend - I'm in [Using PhoneProUsa] South California"

 ..and you may be lucky not to get kicked off.

