@NODE REQ "Requirements"

System Requirements
ĮĮĮĮĮĮĮĮĮĮĮĮĮĮĮĮĮĮĮ
This program has been tested on an Amiga 1200 without fast ram, and an
A1200 with a 68ec030 / 40mhz with 4mb fast ram. It works fine.

This minimum this little utility requires is an Amiga computer equipped
with at least Kickstart version 2.00+, so all you A500/1500/2000 owners
will have to upgrade sooner or later. You must also have the reqtools
library in your libs: directory. 

This program MAY work on KS1.3- but do not count on it, KS1.3 has lots of
bugs and several missing features that this program uses such as sleeping
in the menu and public screens.

