@NODE HIST "History"

History
ĮĮĮĮĮĮĮ
This is the history of Phone Pro Usa from the oldest to the newest (this
order is better than the standard format as you can see how it progressed).

v1.00 First Public Release

    Very, very small, killed the system and opened an non-standard screen,
very poor even though I didn't create it [Jam]. I could also mention that
was first created in Amos.

v2.00 - v2.37 Internal updates.

    Changed from Amos to Amiga E.

v2.38 New public Release 

    Amiga E format allowed it to open on a public/workbench screen. Much
faster and efficient to use.

v2.39 Internal Update

    Fixed a bug when PPUsa opens on a pubscreen.

v3.00 New Public Release

    Many more additions, Vectorchecks, self-Pubscreen opening, system info.

